<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4604338>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Photos of the holotype CIBYN201909290 of Megophrys lushuiensis sp. nov. in life. A, dorsal view. B, ventral view. C, lateral view. D, ventral view of hand. E, ventral view of foot. F, maxillary view, noting vomerine ridges weak and vomerine teeth absent." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4604338/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4604340>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Photos of the holotype specimen CIBYN201909290 of Megophrys lushuiensis sp. nov. A, dorsal view. B, ventral view. C, lateral view of head. D, ventral view of hand. E, ventral view of foot." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4604340/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4604342>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Color variation in Megophrys lushuiensis sp. nov. in life.A and B, dorsolateral and ventral view of adult male paratype CIBYN201909283, SVL 31.0 mm, respectively. C and D, dorsolateral view of two juveniles in situ, SVL 17.8‾18.7 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4604342/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4604344>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Photos of the tadpole CIBYN201909171 of Megophrys lushuiensis sp. nov. in life.A, dorsal view. B, lateral view. C, ventral view. D, dorsal view of head." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4604344/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4604346>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Habitats of Megophrys lushuiensis sp. nov. in the type locality, Lushui County, Yunnan Province, China. A, landscape for forest. B, the stream under the forest." ;
